1.8
log
@Fix comments telling that the `serial mode' bit in PSR only applies to 88110,
it also exists on 88100. While there, do not allow userland to set it.
@
text
@/*	$OpenBSD: psl.h,v 1.7 2011/03/23 16:54:35 pirofti Exp $ */
